qas.question: What group awarded Schwarzenegger the title of one of the 11 "worst governors" in a 2010 report?

answers.text: Citizens for Responsibility and Ethics in Washington

context: In its April 2010 report, Progressive ethics watchdog group <a0_0>Citizens for Responsibility and Ethics in Washington<a0_0/> named Schwarzenegger one of 11 "worst governors" in the United States because of various ethics issues throughout Schwarzenegger's term as governor.
